---
// Back-to-back N-channel MOSFETs (charge + discharge FET) — typical BMS topology
---
<figure class="not-prose rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 600 280" class="w-full" role="img" aria-label="Back-to-back N-channel MOSFETs forming a bidirectional switch in a BMS">
    <rect x="1" y="1" width="598" height="278" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />
    <text x="14" y="20" font-size="11" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" fill="#0f172a">Back-to-back N-channel — BMS 표준 양방향 스위치</text>

    <!-- Battery (left) -->
    <rect x="30" y="100" width="50" height="80" fill="#10b981" stroke="#047857" />
    <text x="40" y="145" font-size="10" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">BAT</text>
    <text x="32" y="200" font-size="9" fill="#047857" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">+ 배터리 −</text>

    <!-- BAT+ wire -->
    <line x1="80" y1="120" x2="160" y2="120" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <text x="100" y="115" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">B+</text>

    <!-- Q1 (Discharge FET) -->
    <g>
      <rect x="160" y="80" width="80" height="80" fill="#fbbf24" stroke="#92400e" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="180" y="105" font-size="10" fill="#92400e" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Q1</text>
      <text x="170" y="120" font-size="8" fill="#92400e" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">DSG</text>
      <!-- D (drain) on top, S (source) on bottom -->
      <line x1="200" y1="80" x2="200" y2="60" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="205" y="65" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">D</text>
      <line x1="200" y1="160" x2="200" y2="180" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="205" y="175" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">S</text>
      <!-- Body diode (drain-to-source, anode at S, cathode at D) -->
      <polygon points="220,108 230,118 220,128" fill="none" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1" />
      <line x1="218" y1="108" x2="218" y2="128" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1" />
      <line x1="232" y1="108" x2="232" y2="128" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1" />
      <text x="245" y="125" font-size="8" fill="#dc2626" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">body diode</text>
      <!-- Gate -->
      <line x1="160" y1="120" x2="140" y2="120" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="125" y="125" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">G</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Wire connecting Q1.S to Q2.S (sources tied together) -->
    <line x1="200" y1="180" x2="200" y2="200" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="380" y2="200" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <line x1="380" y1="200" x2="380" y2="180" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />

    <!-- Q2 (Charge FET) -->
    <g>
      <rect x="340" y="80" width="80" height="80" fill="#fbbf24" stroke="#92400e" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="360" y="105" font-size="10" fill="#92400e" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Q2</text>
      <text x="370" y="120" font-size="8" fill="#92400e" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">CHG</text>
      <line x1="380" y1="80" x2="380" y2="60" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="385" y="65" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">D</text>
      <line x1="380" y1="160" x2="380" y2="180" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="385" y="175" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">S</text>
      <polygon points="320,108 310,118 320,128" fill="none" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1" />
      <line x1="322" y1="108" x2="322" y2="128" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1" />
      <line x1="308" y1="108" x2="308" y2="128" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1" />
      <line x1="420" y1="120" x2="440" y2="120" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="445" y="125" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">G</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Q1.D up to load -->
    <line x1="200" y1="60" x2="200" y2="40" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="380" y2="40" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <line x1="380" y1="40" x2="380" y2="60" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <text x="280" y="35" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">PACK +</text>

    <!-- Load (right) -->
    <line x1="380" y1="40" x2="500" y2="40" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />
    <rect x="500" y="100" width="60" height="80" fill="#0f172a" />
    <text x="510" y="145" font-size="10" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">LOAD</text>
    <text x="500" y="200" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">/ Charger</text>
    <line x1="500" y1="40" x2="500" y2="100" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="2" />

    <!-- BAT- to LOAD- (return path) -->
    <line x1="80" y1="170" x2="500" y2="170" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 3" />
    <line x1="500" y1="170" x2="500" y2="180" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 3" />
    <text x="240" y="165" font-size="9" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">B− / GND (return)</text>

    <!-- Annotations -->
    <text x="14" y="245" font-size="10" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">• Q1 (DSG) 가 OFF → 방전 차단 (body diode 가 충전은 통과)</text>
    <text x="14" y="260" font-size="10" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">• Q2 (CHG) 가 OFF → 충전 차단 (body diode 가 방전은 통과)</text>
    <text x="14" y="275" font-size="10" fill="#475569" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">• 두 FET 의 source 가 묶여 있으면 gate 기준이 같아 driver 단순</text>
  </svg>
</figure>
